sections.content:
**Platform**: Android (AAR). iOS / JVM desktop / Python / Node.js / C bindings are on the roadmap.

**Artifact**: `pinelabs-sdk-0.1.0.aar` (local file)

Add to `app/build.gradle`:

```gradle
android {
    defaultConfig {
        minSdk 21
        ndk { abiFilters 'arm64-v8a', 'armeabi-v7a', 'x86_64' }
    }
}

dependencies {
    implementation files('libs/pinelabs-sdk-0.1.0.aar')
    implementation 'com.google.code.gson:gson:2.10.1'
    implementation 'net.java.dev.jna:jna:5.14.0@aar'
    implementation 'org.jetbrains.kotlinx:kotlinx-coroutines-android:1.7.3'
}
```

ProGuard / R8 keep rules:

```
-keep class uniffi.pinelabs.** { *; }
-keep class com.pinelabs.sdk.** { *; }
-keep class com.sun.jna.** { *; }
```
